载Linux系统镜像</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8vmware%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E5%AF%BC%E5%90%91"><span class="toc-number">3.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">第三步：启动vmware创建虚拟机导向</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85"><span class="toc-number">3.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">第四步：进入系统完成安装</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%BF%9E%E9%80%9A%E6%80%A7"><span class="toc-number">3.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">第五步：测试网络连通性</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E9%A2%9D%E5%A4%96%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C"><span class="toc-number">3.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">额外操作</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86"><span class="toc-number">3.6.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">快照管理</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%85%8B%E9%9A%86"><span class="toc-number">3.6.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">克隆</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#Linux%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86"><span class="toc-number">4.</span> <span class="toc-text">Linux文件与目录管理</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D"><span class="toc-number">4.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">目录结构介绍</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86"><span class="toc-number">4.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">文件查看与处理</span></a