5%B3%E6%9C%BA-%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AF"><span class="toc-number">10.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">Linux关机&#x2F;重启</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#Linux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E4%B8%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97"><span class="toc-number">10.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">Linux系统监视与日志</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#Linux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90"><span class="toc-number">11.</span> <span class="toc-text">Linux系统启动过程分析</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#Linux%E7%9A%84Shell%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80"><span class="toc-number">12.</span> <span class="toc-text">Linux的Shell基础</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AFShell%EF%BC%9F"><span class="toc-number">12.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">什么是Shell？</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%87%A0%E4%B8%AA%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%BE%A8%E6%9E%90"><span class="toc-number">12.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">几个概念辨析</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#Shell%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%B1%BB"><span class="toc-number">12.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">Shell的种类</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8shell%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E5%AE%9A"><span class="toc-number">12.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">用户使用shell的设定</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8BLinux%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%9A%84Shell"><span class="toc-number">12.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">查看Linux安装的Shell</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#Linux%E7%9A%84Shell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B"><span class="toc-number">13.</span> <span class="toc-text">Linux的Shell脚本编程</span></a><ol cla